In today's market, the demand to improve the strategic use of information technology and to maximize price/performance ratios is driving companies of all sizes to consider cloud computing and open source platforms as compelling alternatives to proprietary technologies.

JC Kelly provides a full range of data, telephony, Internet and consulting services to accelerate and enhance the adoption of cloud based and open source solutions in small and medium sized businesses. We help organizations to assess how to successfully deploy and integrate these technologies with proprietary systems.
